title: Roxy Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Restaurant in the main drag of downtown that offers a falafel burger and has hummus, grape leaves, pasta, veg burrito, pizza, and other food. Kitchen is open to creating a custom veg option or meal upon request. Located next door to Ecotopiia eco shop. Confirmed open Aug 2015.
